{"tid":698690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[內含圖文詳細分析]講真TL真係deserve比Kwan gor同牙Fred更高既地位","createTime":"2018-06-12T02:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T12:46:25.000Z","uid":5006,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c227224ae8fed16fd68404713c350c68b1c717c","tid":698690,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"一個歌星實力建基於曲風、歌路，同埋歌唱技巧、形象。<br />\nTL呢4維能力都比另外兩位樂壇新星過之而無不及！<br />\n<br />\n1. 曲風：<br />\n坤哥兩個都係靠慢歌上位就唔洗多講，<br />\n牙FRED受電視劇主題曲曲風所限，黎黎去去都係POP ROCK風。<br />\n而TL快慢兼備，亦追上而家時興既EDM，<br />\n主打歌曲Party with TL完全緊扣著世界熱潮EDM曲風，<br />\n明顯比另外兩位走得更前！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：<br />\nFred - 3/5<br />\n坤哥 - 4/5<br />\nTL - 5/5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/101031_de339f4a617333fe38d69d12775412ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F101031_de339f4a617333fe38d69d12775412ac.gif&h=2d0ffb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 歌路：<br />\nFred係靠電視劇主題曲為人所知，都係市場主題既歌曲，歌路大多為情歌。<br />\n坤哥亦主要係情歌同埋兵歌，不過最近想轉下形象，<br />\n加左首精裝追女仔，有大膽革新既嘗試！<br />\nTL既歌絕非只停留一般既情歌路線，<br />\n當中有多係自己既反思同埋堅持，<br />\n燴炙人口既歌詞：「Man 我只想做好自己」可見一班，<br />\n又例如「反省」咁，實係樂壇一大清泉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：<br />\nFred - 2/5<br />\n坤哥 - 3.5/5<br />\nTL - 4/5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/101858_6451d4f233f0d9c5790bd818a4b593dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F101858_6451d4f233f0d9c5790bd818a4b593dd.png&h=cc3ab86e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/100943_87d2fb30e3a741610609505a2d013194.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F100943_87d2fb30e3a741610609505a2d013194.gif&h=cd07d2bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 歌唱技巧：<br />\n牙FRED不嬲比人點評比較浮誇，唔係人人都受到。<br />\n坤哥唱LIVE有分咁上下，<br />\n但係佢本人都話過比人批評過有人話佢唱歌好似比人摙緊下面咁，<br />\n證明都唔係能討好每個人！<br />\nTL唱LIVE可以駕馭到跳同唱而不索氣，已經可見其實力派既能力，連陳詠謙都撐佢咁話！<br />\n雖然因為歌詞中英夾雜未能做到每個咬字都十分清晰，<br />\n但同另外兩位歌手一樣有進步空間！所以呢PART打和！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：<br />\nFred：3.5/5<br />\n坤哥：3.5/5<br />\nTL：3.5/5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRTatRIdpIc69Yx7L1Zm3RNQGg_kGbAt2AObFNQjCkKDZDffoDzOA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRTatRIdpIc69Yx7L1Zm3RNQGg_kGbAt2AObFNQjCkKDZDffoDzOA&h=2c922f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/101512_ec7c7569860b42adc4861318caaeb198.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F101512_ec7c7569860b42adc4861318caaeb198.gif&h=045b7c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 形象：<br />\n唔洗我多講，牙FRED有老婆偷食已經一鋪清袋，<br />\n地位同街邊上樓叫雞既呀伯無咩分別。<br />\n連無線史詩劇集逆緣都無埋佢份就知形象幾差！<br />\n坤哥偽毒食女都人盡皆知，上晒雜誌連佢自己都自嘲！<br />\n相反TL即使入過冊，出黎都要堅持拎老豆遺產追夢，<br />\n呢股毅力值得年青人學習！<br />\n唔講唔知，佢仲去過老人院派啲月餅比啲呀公呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢可以成為繼學友同E神成為新一代「更生歌神」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：<br />\nFRED：1/5<br />\n坤歌：2/5<br />\nTL：4.5/5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nvsay.com/uploads/allimg/160505/42-1605051444312W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nvsay.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F160505%2F42-1605051444312W.jpg&h=c0432ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=slac1j/30484e796b7a644f3866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3Dslac1j%2F30484e796b7a644f3866.jpg&h=8e2db294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170209/large/09ec4p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170209%2Flarge%2F09ec4p12.jpg&h=0d3350a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 總結<br />\n<br />\n總分：<br />\nFRED：9.5/20<br />\n坤哥：13/20<br />\nTL：17/20<br />\n<br />\n睇完詳情既分析可見TL值得更多既尊重同埋支持！<br />\n樂壇前輩林敏聰曾經話過香港樂壇倒退其中一個主因係無晒D STAR，<br />\n以前陳百強、梅姐、呀麟果D粒粒巨星，<br />\n但坤哥、牙Fred呢D實力派歌手實在太平凡！<br />\n所以比心機，TL，希望你可以成為香港樂壇既明日之星！"},{"pid":"57d7407007be5023f86dc27f817fe5a62353a2df","tid":698690,"uid":7099,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:36:51.000Z","msg":"個個都玩完樓主先打咁大篇野出黎 有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400986e02989185f66587ed44817765a5f00878d","tid":698690,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"bd5e5830f71a1906d49a2ac99defe0333c726304","tid":698690,"uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57d7407007be5023f86dc27f817fe5a62353a2df","tid":698690,"uid":7099,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:36:51.000Z","msg":"個個都玩完樓主先打咁大篇野出黎 有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:38:43.000Z","msg":"好想比啲支持TL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人推到比TL本人睇<br />\n話晒都打左成粒鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d07eb546ef187200c93c069c9ea97f8ade37c5b","tid":698690,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個都玩完樓主先打咁大篇野出